    - SAUCE: apparmor: Fix no_new_privs blocking change_onexec when using stacked
      namespaces

  * apparmor_parser hangs indefinitely when called by multiple threads
    (LP: #1645037)
    - SAUCE: apparmor: fix lock ordering for mkdir

